Unbound is a validating, recursive, caching DNS resolver. It is
designed to be fast and lean and incorporates modern features based on
open standards.

User / Group
------------

To run unbound without root privileges you must add the following user
and group:

  # /usr/sbin/groupadd -g 304 unbound
  # /usr/sbin/useradd -d /var/lib/unbound -s /sbin/nologin -u 304 \
      -g unbound unbound
